OL,3,CBrothers go on trial over alleged
OL,4,Caltercation with police at airport
OL,6,FA judge told potential jurors in the
OL,7,Ftrial of two brothers alleged to have
OL,8,Fbeen involved in an altercation with
OL,9,Fpolice at Manchester Airport that they
OL,10,F"must not be influenced" by the
OL,11,Fmainstream media or social media.
OL,13,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 20, and Muhammad
OL,14,FAmaad, 26, both of Tarnside Close in
OL,15,FRochdale, appeared at Liverpool Crown
OL,16,FCourt on Monday, 30 June.
OL,18,FThey are charged with assault
OL,19,Ffollowing video footage of an alleged
OL,20,Fincident involving police officers and
OL,21,Fmembers of the public in July 2024.
