OL,4,Caltercation with police at airport
OL,6,FA panel of 40 jurors was reduced to 28
OL,7,Fafter the panel was asked to complete
OL,8,Fa questionnaire.
OL,10,FAs jury selection began, Judge Neil
OL,11,FFlewitt KC told the panel: "You will
OL,12,Fhave realised from the questionnaire
OL,13,Fthis trial involves events at
OL,14,FManchester Airport on 23 July which
OL,15,Fattracted a large amount of mainstream
OL,16,Fand social media interest."
OL,18,FHe added that as the trial progresses
OL,19,Fthere was likely to be further media
OL,20,Fcomment.
