OL,3,CBrothers go on trial over alleged
OL,4,Caltercation with police at airport
OL,6,FHe went on: "You must reach your
OL,7,Fverdicts in this trial based on the
OL,8,Fevidence presented in court and you
OL,9,Fmust not allow yourselves to be
OL,10,Finfluenced by anything you may have
OL,11,Fread or heard on the mainstream media
OL,12,For social media."
OL,14,FJudge Flewitt urged the panel not to
OL,15,Flook up any information about the case
OL,16,Fon the internet until they returned on
OL,17,FWednesday morning to resume jury
OL,18,Fselection.
