OL,3,CBrothers go on trial over alleged
OL,4,Caltercation with police at airport
OL,6,FMr Amaaz is charged with assaulting a
OL,7,Fmember of the public by beating him on
OL,8,F23 July 2024 at Manchester Airport.
OL,10,FHe also faces a second charge that he
OL,11,Fassaulted a police officer causing
OL,12,Factual bodily harm on the same date,
OL,13,Falso at Manchester Airport.
OL,15,FA third charge alleges he assaulted PC
OL,16,FLydia Ward causing actual bodily harm
OL,17,Fon the same date at the airport.
OL,19,FA fourth charge against him alleges he
OL,20,Fassaulted, by beating, an emergency
OL,21,Fworker, PC Ellie Cook.
