OL,6,FHis co defendant Muhammad Amaad, his
OL,7,Fbrother, faces a single charge, namely
OL,8,Fthat he assaulted PC Zachary Marsden
OL,9,Fat Manchester Airport on July 23.JThe
OL,10,Ftrial is scheduled to last three weeks.
